---
name: query_warehouse
description: >
  Run a safe read-only SQL query against the internal analytics warehouse.
  The warehouse pre-joins Shopify product/inventory data with Google Ads
  campaign performance. Use for cross-platform questions like "which campaigns
  are spending on out-of-stock products" or "POAS by SKU". Available tables:
  warehouse_shopify_products (sku, title, inventory_qty, price, cogs),
  warehouse_google_ads (campaign_name, cost_usd, conversions, clicks,
  impressions), warehouse_cross_platform_mapping (google_ad_id,
  shopify_product_id, sku). Views: v_ads_on_empty_shelves, v_poas_by_sku.
---
Read-only SELECT only. Use for cross-platform joins the dedicated tools don't cover.
